  "method": [
    "Heat oil in a skillet over the medium heat.",
    "Put the onion in it and cook for around 5 minutes.",
    "Then add oregano, garlic, and cumin. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add cauliflower in a dishtowel and drain any excess liquid.",
    "Add more oil if required, and add grated cauliflower, pepper, and salt.",
    "Stir occasionally while cooking.",
    "Add the tomato paste, black beans, chicken, tomatoes, corn,",
    "coriander, and jalapenos.",
    "Add cheeses over it, then cover and cook until it melts.",
    "Serve and Enjoy!"
